<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Icon Manager – Social Media Icon Management Made Simple</title>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 60px 20px 40px;
        background: #0d6efd;
        color: #fff;
    }
    header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    header p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .cta-btn {
        background: #ffc107;
        color: #000;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .section {
        padding: 50px 20px;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: auto;
    }
    .section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #0d6efd;
    }
    .features {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
    }
    .feature {
        background: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    .feature h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #0d6efd;
    }
    .pricing {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 20px;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    .price-plan {
        background: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        flex: 1;
        min-width: 250px;
        max-width: 300px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .price-plan h3 {
        color: #0d6efd;
    }
    .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #0d6efd;
        color: white;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Icon Manager</h1>
    <p>Manage and update your website’s social media icons instantly — from one dashboard.</p>
    <button class="cta-btn">Get Started Free</button>
</header>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Why Icon Manager?</h2>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>One Dashboard</h3>
            <p>Update social icons across all your websites without touching code.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Works Everywhere</h3>
            <p>Compatible with WordPress, Wix, Shopify, Drupal, static sites, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Customizable Styles</h3>
            <p>Choose from a variety of icon designs, colors, and sizes to match your brand.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Instant Updates</h3>
            <p>Changes go live instantly — no redeployment or technical skills needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Analytics Built-in</h3>
            <p>Track clicks and engagement across all your social icons.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Pricing</h2>
    <div class="pricing">
        <div class="price-plan">
            <h3>Free</h3>
            <p>$0/month</p>
            <p>1 site, up to 3 icons</p>
            <button class="cta-btn">Sign Up</button>
        </div>
        <div class="price-plan">
            <h3>Pro</h3>
            <p>$9/month</p>
            <p>Unlimited icons, analytics, custom styles</p>
            <button class="cta-btn">Upgrade</button>
        </div>
        <div class="price-plan">
            <h3>Agency</h3>
            <p>$29/month</p>
            <p>Manage up to 10 sites</p>
            <button class="cta-btn">Contact Us</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="footer">
    <p>© 2025 Icon Manager. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
